column3: "How long have you been waiting for your mommy?"
"have you heard or seen anything strange happening here"
"Why... why would you do this to these innocent people?"
"I think we both know that isn't happening"
*does a boss impression* "Its time to head home"
"Whats going on with your freind over there?"
"your not just faking it like the other gaurd right?"
"man you have been doing a crappy job around here"
"what weird things does a janitor see around this place?"
"do you know how I could get into some of these locked doors?"
"Is there anything I can do to help?"
"is there anything you can do to help me?"
"can you at least tell me what wierd things you have seen around this place?"
